Class UserModifiableConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thinkaurelius.titan.diskstorage.configuration.UserModifiableConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TitanConfiguration
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TitanFactory.Builder

    public class UserModifiableConfiguration
extends Object
implements TitanConfiguration
    Helper class for inspecting and modifying a configuration for Titan. It is important to close() the configuration when all changes have been made.
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
